column5: hey yall ive noticed at the show they have the new diawa megaforce for like 60 bux! quantum code is there for 80, did anyone pick up the diawa? what do u think? perhaps for senkos and other plastics maybe good i hear

Hey bud, You will be surprised in that reel. Great reel for the money. Little on the heavy side but for $60 you will not go wrong. I bought them last fall in the US and have used them and they are great.
